from fastai.vision.all import *
import geopandas as gpd
from tqdm import tqdm
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from collections import Counter

dls = ImageDataLoaders.from_name_func(
    path="/home/jovyan/home/training7",
    fnames=files,
    label_func=label_func,
    item_tfms=Resize(224),
    batch_tfms=[*aug_transforms(xtra_tfms=None)],
    splitter=my_splitter
)

# Get labels for training and validation
train_labels = [dls.vocab[o[1]] for o in dls.train_ds]
valid_labels = [dls.vocab[o[1]] for o in dls.valid_ds]

# Count occurrences
train_counts = Counter(train_labels)
valid_counts = Counter(valid_labels)

# Prepare data for plotting
labels = dls.vocab
train_vals = [train_counts.get(lbl, 0) for lbl in labels]
valid_vals = [valid_counts.get(lbl, 0) for lbl in labels]

# Plot
x = range(len(labels))
plt.figure(figsize=(10,5))
plt.bar(x, train_vals, width=0.4, label="Train")
plt.bar([i+0.4 for i in x], valid_vals, width=0.4, label="Valid")
plt.xticks([i+0.2 for i in x], labels, rotation=45)
plt.xlabel("Labels")
plt.ylabel("Count")
plt.title("Label repartition in Train vs Validation")
plt.legend()
plt.show()
